{"thag2.37:0.1":"Theragatha 2.37 ","thag2.37:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.37:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.37:0.4":"Sonapotiriyattheragatha ","thag2.37:1.1":"“Na tava supitum hoti, ","thag2.37:1.2":"ratti nakkhattamalini; ","thag2.37:1.3":"Patijaggitumevesa, ","thag2.37:1.4":"ratti hoti vijanata”. ","thag2.37:2.1":"“Hatthikkhandhavapatitam, ","thag2.37:2.2":"kunjaro ce anukkame; ","thag2.37:2.3":"Sangame me matam seyyo, ","thag2.37:2.4":"yance jive parajito”ti. ","thag2.37:2.5":"… Sono potiriyo thero …. "}